<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3154984" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="U" oldref="4">Illumination</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3155391" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="5">Specify the light source for the object, as well as the color of the light source and of the ambient light. You can define up to eight different light sources.</paragraph>
